"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?41/17/42258?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Ulcerative colitis in adults (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
